Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:55.89,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,240)}誰ももういない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:22:59.61,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,240)}約束だなんて
